                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18170917-13-off70 t18170917-13-cd71"></join>, one watch, value 2l.; one chain, value 6d., and one key, value 1d., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18170917-13-victim149" type="victimName">
                           Jabez 
                           Trotman
